originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    c.kind AS company_type,
    COUNT(ci.person_id) AS total_cast,
    AVG(CAST(mi.info AS numeric)) AS avg_movie_rating
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    aka_title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_type c ON mc.company_type_id = c.id
JOIN 
    movie_info mi ON t.id = mi.movie_id
WHERE 
    t.production_year > 2000
    AND c.kind = 'Production'
GROUP BY 
    a.name, t.title, c.kind, mi.info
HAVING 
    COUNT(ci.person_id) > 3
ORDER BY 
    avg_movie_rating DESC, total_cast DESC
LIMIT 10

FROM (SELECT "aka_name"."name", "s1"."title", 'Production' AS "kind", "movie_info"."info", ANY_VALUE("aka_name"."name") AS "ACTOR_NAME", ANY_VALUE("s1"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", ANY_VALUE("t1"."kind") AS "COMPANY_TYPE", COUNT(*) AS "TOTAL_CAST", AVG(CAST("movie_info"."info" AS DECIMAL(19, 0))) AS "AVG_MOVIE_RATING"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "company_type"
WHERE "kind" = 'Production') AS "t1"
INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id" INNER JOIN ("movie_info" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "movie_info"."movie_id" = "s1"."id") ON "cast_info"."movie_id" = "s1"."id") ON "t1"."id" = "s1"."company_type_id"
GROUP BY "aka_name"."name", "s1"."title", "movie_info"."info") AS "t4"
WHERE "t4"."TOTAL_CAST" > 3
ORDER BY "AVG_MOVIE_RATING" DESC NULLS FIRST, "TOTAL_CAST" DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t7"

SELECT COALESCE("ACTOR_NAME", "ACTOR_NAME") AS "ACTOR_NAME", "MOVIE_TITLE", "COMPANY_TYPE", "TOTAL_CAST", "AVG_MOVIE_RATING"

FROM (SELECT *
FROM "company_type"
WHERE "kind" = 'Production') AS "t0"
INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id" INNER JOIN ("movie_info" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *

GROUP BY "aka_name"."name", "t1"."title", "movie_info"."info") AS "t4"
WHERE "t4"."TOTAL_CAST" > 3
ORDER BY "AVG_MOVIE_RATING" DESC NULLS FIRST, "TOTAL_CAST" DESC NULLS FIRST

FROM (SELECT *
FROM "company_type"
WHERE "kind" = 'Production') AS "t0"
INNER JOIN ("aka_name" INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_name"."person_id" = "cast_info"."person_id" INNER JOIN ("movie_info" INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "aka_title"

GROUP BY "aka_name"."name", "t1"."title", "movie_info"."info") AS "t4"
